
Version 1.0
 - Upgraded to use jQuery 1.7 (breaks plugin for older versions of jQ)
 - Changed structure of plugin code to use objects (complete code restructuring)
 - Changed structure of PHP code to use class/methods (complete code restructuring)
 - Added better events
 - Added ability to "refresh" the captcha options (manually and by user button click)
 - Added testing suite

Version 0.2
 - Changed to use title attribute of image for hash (versus alt) (We don't want the hash showing as images load)
 - Fixed simpleCaptcha.php to return properly formatted JSON (fixes bug in jQuery 1.4)

Version 0.1
 - Initial Release